'''坦納·B·羅亞克'''（{{lang-en|Tanner B. Roark}}，{{IPAc-en|r|oʊ|ˈ|ɑr|k}} {{respell|roh|ARK|'}}，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.masnsports.com/nationals-pastime/2014/02/final-notes-and-quotes-plus-day-4-photo-gallery.html |title=Kolko, Dan. "Final notes and quotes, plus Day 4 photo gallery," masnsports.com, Tuesday, February 18, 2014. |access-date=2021-03-07 |archive-date=2019-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630215623/https://www.masnsports.com/nationals-pastime/2014/02/final-notes-and-quotes-plus-day-4-photo-gallery.html }}</ref>{{bd|1986年|10月5日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的投手，目前為自由球員。他先前曾效力過國民、紅人、運動家與藍鳥等隊。
==職業生涯==
===華盛頓國民===
[[Image:Roark-vs-NYM-20151004.jpg|thumb]]
2013年8月7日，羅亞克登上大聯盟。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.masnsports.com/nationals_pastime/2013/08/nats-promote-tanner-roark-option-cedeno-move-detwiler-to-60-day-dl.html |title="Nats promote Tanner Roark, option Cedeno, move Detwiler to 60-day DL," MASN Sports, August 6, 2013 |access-date=2021-03-07 |archive-date=2013-09-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921053833/http://www.masnsports.com/nationals_pastime/2013/08/nats-promote-tanner-roark-option-cedeno-move-detwiler-to-60-day-dl.html }}</ref>他在1個月後完成他生涯首場先發，並拿下首勝。<ref>{{cite web|title=Tanner Roark 2013 Pitching Gamelogs|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.cgi?id=roarkta01&t=p&year=2013|publisher=Baseball Reference|access-date=September 9, 2013|archive-date=2017-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170209182808/http://www.baseball-reference.com/players/gl.cgi?id=roarkta01&t=p&year=2013}}</ref>整年他拿下7勝1敗，防禦率1.08。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://stats.washingtonpost.com/mlb/playerstats.asp?id=9484&fn=Tanner&ln=Roark&team=20&p=T&page=logs|title=Baseball | MLB | Player stats - Tanner Roark - Washington|work=The Washington Post|access-date=September 19, 2013|archive-date=2019-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610211253/http://stats.washingtonpost.com/mlb/playerstats.asp?id=9484&fn=Tanner&ln=Roark&team=20&p=T&page=logs}}</ref><ref name=autogenerated1>{{Cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/r/roarkta01.shtml |title=Tanner Roark Stats {{!}} Baseball-Reference.com<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2021-03-07 |archive-date=2021-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210708031009/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/r/roarkta01.shtml }}</ref>

2014年4月26日，羅亞克拿下生涯首場完投完封勝。整年他拿下15勝10敗，防禦率2.85。<ref name=autogenerated1 />隔年他拿下4勝7敗，防禦率4.38。<ref name=autogenerated1 />

[[File:Tanner_Roark_pitches,_viewed_from_LF_corner,_July_13,_2018_(cropped).jpg|left]]
2016年，他拿下16勝，防禦率2.83，172次三振都是個人生涯新高。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=2&season=2016&month=0&season1=2016&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=20,a |title=Major League Leaderboards » 2016 » Pitchers » Batted Ball Statistics {{!}} FanGraphs Baseball<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2021-03-07 |archive-date=2018-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181227040704/https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=2&season=2016&month=0&season1=2016&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&sort=20,a }}</ref>2017年，他拿下13勝11敗，防禦率4.67。<ref name=autogenerated1 />隔年他拿下9勝15敗，防禦率4.34。<ref name=autogenerated1 />
===辛辛那提紅人===
2018年12月12日，國民用羅亞克向紅人交易Tanner Rainey。2019年1月11日，紅人與羅亞克達成1年1000萬美元的協議。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/25520483/washington-nationals-trade-tanner-roark-cincinnati-reds-tanner-rainey |title=Washington Nationals trade Tanner Roark to Cincinnati Reds for Tanner Rainey<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2021-03-07 |archive-date=2021-05-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210504094739/https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/25520483/washington-nationals-trade-tanner-roark-cincinnati-reds-tanner-rainey }}</ref> On January 11, 2019, the Reds signed Roark to a one-year contract worth $10 million, avoiding arbitration.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cbssports.com/fantasy/baseball/news/reds-tanner-roark-comes-to-terms-with-cincy/ |title=Reds' Tanner Roark: Comes to terms with Cincy<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2021-03-07 |archive-date=2019-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190415081530/https://www.cbssports.com/fantasy/baseball/news/reds-tanner-roark-comes-to-terms-with-cincy/ }}</ref>

2019年上半季，羅亞克在紅人拿下6勝7敗，防禦率4.24。
===奧克蘭運動家===
2019年7月31日，紅人用羅亞克向運動家交易來Jameson Hannah。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/athletics/press-release/a-s-acquire-rhp-tanner-roark-from-cincinnati-for-minor-league-of-jameson-hannah|title=A's Acquire RHP Tanner Roark from Cincinnati for Minor League OF Jameson Hannah|work=MLB.com|date=July 31, 2019|access-date=2021-03-07|archive-date=2019-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190731225112/https://www.mlb.com/athletics/press-release/a-s-acquire-rhp-tanner-roark-from-cincinnati-for-minor-league-of-jameson-hannah}}</ref>而他在這年被敲出平飛安打的機率高達17.1%，為全大聯盟投手最高。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fangraphs.com/leaders.aspx?pos=all&stats=pit&lg=all&qual=y&type=2&season=2019&month=0&season1=2019&ind=0&team=0&rost=0&age=0&filter=&players=0&startdate=2019-01-01&enddate=2019-12-31&sort=5,a |title=Major League Leaderboards » 2019 » Pitchers » Batted Ball Statistics | FanGraphs Baseball |publisher=Fangraphs.com |date=January 1, 2019 |access-date=October 10, 2019}}</ref>
===多倫多藍鳥===
2019年12月18日，他和藍鳥隊簽下2年2400萬美元的合約。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/bluejays/news/tanner-roark-signs-with-blue-jays|title=Roark, Blue Jays finalize 2-year deal|publisher=Toronto Blue Jays|date=December 18, 2019|access-date=December 18, 2019|archive-date=2021-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210318004843/https://www.mlb.com/bluejays/news/tanner-roark-signs-with-blue-jays}}</ref>2020年他出賽11場比賽，拿下2勝3敗，防禦率6.80。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlb.com/player/tanner-roark-543699 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-07 |archive-date=2021-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317173511/https://www.mlb.com/player/tanner-roark-543699 }}</ref>

2021年，羅亞克在前三場先發的防禦率高達6.43，因此他在4月30日被球隊放進指定讓渡名單內，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/04/blue-jays-designate-tanner-roark-for-assignment.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-05-09 |archive-date=2021-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501142906/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/04/blue-jays-designate-tanner-roark-for-assignment.html }}</ref>並於5月3日遭到釋出。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/05/tanner-roark-clears-waivers-becomes-free-agent.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-05-09 |archive-date=2021-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210520180630/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/05/tanner-roark-clears-waivers-becomes-free-agent.html }}</ref>
===亞特蘭大勇士===
2021年5月10日，他和勇士隊簽下小聯盟合約。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/05/braves-to-sign-tanner-roark-to-minor-league-deal.html/email|title=Braves To Sign Tanner Roark To Minor League Deal|author=Anthony Franco|date=May 10, 2021|access-date=2021-07-16|archive-date=2021-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210510190553/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/05/braves-to-sign-tanner-roark-to-minor-league-deal.html/email}}</ref>6月24日，他入選球隊26人名單內。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/06/braves-select-jesse-chavez.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-07-16 |archive-date=2021-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210703024550/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/06/braves-select-jesse-chavez.html }}</ref>不過他在勇士隊沒有登上大聯盟，他在3A留下2.14的防禦率之後，於9月5日成為自由球員。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/09/tanner-roark-elects-free-agency.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-10-10 |archive-date=2022-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220426112948/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2021/09/tanner-roark-elects-free-agency.html }}</ref>
==國際賽==
2017年，因為[[麥斯·薛澤|麥斯·薛澤]]受傷，因此羅亞克遞補代表美國隊參加世界棒球經典賽。受到球團規定，他最多在一場比賽只能投50球。他在四強賽先發對決日本隊，他主投4局無失分，最後美國隊2比1贏球，隊史首度闖進經典賽冠軍賽。美國隊總教練Jim Leyland也公開讚賞羅亞克在大賽面前的強心臟與好表現。<ref>{{cite news|last=James|first=Chelsea|title=Tanner Roark throws four scoreless innings for Team USA in WBC Semifinal Win,|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/nationals-journal/wp/2017/03/22/tanner-roark-throws-four-scoreless-innings-for-team-usa-in-wbc-semifinal-win/|access-date=March 23, 2017|newspaper=Washington Post|date=March 22, 2017|archive-date=2019-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190415081532/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/nationals-journal/wp/2017/03/22/tanner-roark-throws-four-scoreless-innings-for-team-usa-in-wbc-semifinal-win/}}</ref>
